abstract: Toledo beats Temple, 32-17, in Boca Raton Bowl; other college football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Phillip Ely hit Cody Thompson with an 80-yard touchdown pass early in the fourth quarter, and Toledo prevailed in Jason Candle’s first game as head coach.

headline.main: Toledo Tops Temple in Boca Bowl
